'''鳥龍鳥科'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|Avisauridae}}）是[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]時期[[北美洲|北美洲]]及[[南美洲|南美洲]]的一[[科|科]][[反鳥亞綱|反鳥亞綱]][[鳥類|鳥類]]<ref name="Chiappe1992">{{Cite journal|author=Chiappe, Luis M|year=1992|title=Enantiornithine (Aves) Tarsometatarsi and the Avian Affinities of the Late Cretaceous Avisauridae|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|volume=12|issue=3|pages=344-50}}</ref>，其下有8個[[屬|屬]]。<ref name="Cau2008">{{Cite journal|author=Cau, A. and Arduini, P.|year=2008|title=Enantiophoenix electrophyla gen. et sp. nov. (Aves, Enantiornithes) from the Upper Cretaceous (Cenomanian) of Lebanon and its phylogenetic relationships|journal=Atti della Società Italiana di Scienze Naturali e del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale in Milano|volume=149|issue=2|pages=293–324}}</ref>

==分類歷史==
鳥龍鳥科是於1985年成立，包含了一些最初被認為是細小[[獸腳亞目|獸腳亞目]][[恐龍|恐龍]]的[[化石|化石]]。<ref name="Brett-Surman&Paul1985">{{Cite journal|author=Brett-Surman, Michael K., Paul, Gregory S|year=1985|title=A new family of bird-like dinosaurs linking Laurasia and Gondwanaland|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|volume=5|issue=2|pages=133-8}}</ref>

[[路易斯·恰佩|路易斯·恰佩]]（Luis M. Chiappe）後來將鳥龍鳥科重置到[[鳥綱|鳥綱]]及反鳥亞綱之下，指它們的第三趾向背面橫凸得很厲害、第三趾滑車內側邊緣明顯突出、及[[蹠骨|蹠骨]]兩側扁平及呈J狀。<ref name= "Chiappe1993">{{Cite journal|author=Chiappe, Luis M|year=1993|title=Enantiornithine (Aves) Tarsometatarsi from the Cretaceous Lecho Formation of Northwestern Argentina|journal=American Museum Novitates|volume=3083|pages=1-2}}</ref>他進一步將鳥龍鳥科定義為[[內烏肯鳥|內烏肯鳥]]及[[鳥龍鳥|鳥龍鳥]]的共同祖先，與及所有後裔。於2008年，鳥龍鳥科重新被定義為鳥龍鳥及所有相關的[[屬|屬]]，而疏於[[長翼鳥|長翼鳥]]、[[戈壁鳥|戈壁鳥]]或[[中國鳥|中國鳥]]。<ref name="Cau2008"/>

