==習性==
恰佩等人發現鳥龍鳥科的拇趾是完全反向及有一大爪，顯示它們可以站在樹上。<ref name="Chiappe&Calvo1994">{{Cite journal|author=Chiappe, Luis M., Calvo, Jorge O|year=1994|title=''Neuquenornis volans'', a New Late Cretaceous Bird (Enantiornithes: Avisauridae) from Patagonia, Argentina|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|volume=14|issue=2|pages=230-46}}</ref>

